description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit a highly motivated Practice Nurse to join our Team.  The ideal candidate would have experience of working in General Practice or Healthcare setting. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Preferably have experience in chronic disease/case management and minor illness.  With nursing skills to carry out the following skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cervical cytology, childhood imms, wound care, phlebotomy, travel imms, ear syringing, minor illness. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate would be required to hold a RGN qualification and have active registration with the NMC, have excellent communication skills with an ability to prioritise your workload and also be a Team player.  Interest in developing their skills by attending relevant training. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hours of work flexible.  Hourly rate negotiable depending on experience. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is subject to references and a satisfactory DSB check.&lt;/p&gt;
